<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.1.2">
<l>ōṭu vārviḻu vārukan tālippār</l>
<l>nāṭu vārnampi rāṉeṅkuṟ ṟāṉeṉpār</l>
<l>pāṭu vārkaḷum palpaṟai koṭṭaniṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṭu vārkaḷu māyiṟṟāyp pāṭiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They run, they fall, rising, they shout,</l>
<l>they seek [him], saying, “where is he, Our Lord?”</l>
<l>The cow-herd hamlet became [filled with] singers,</l>
<l>dancers, and the continuous beating of many drums.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
